data.description: Welcome to your dream coastal retreat! This stunning turnkey home offers the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, close proximity to the ocean and River to Sea Trail. Maritime forests allow you to connect with nature and enjoy wildlife. Situated on a southern facing lot, this home is bathed in natural light throughout the day. Exceptionally constructed with durable concrete, exterior boasts the timeless beauty of St. Augustine pink shell coquina, adding a touch of coastal charm. The kitchen is a gourmet's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, ample counter space for culinary creations. Custom window coverings allow you to control the ambiance effortlessly, the warmth of the gunstock oak floors add a touch of elegance to design. Ensuite bedrooms, 3 screened porches, spa, wine cellar and oversized 2 car garage are just a few of the unique features of the home. Imagine waking up to the sound of ocean and the sight of the forest just beyond your windows! **30 day minimum rentals.
